1. 生成调试信息
    -g 选项
2. 启动gdb
    gdb program
3. 设置参数
    set args arg1 arg2 ...
    show args
4. 设置断点
    break
    4.1 指定函数名 class::function或function(type, type)或namespace::class::function
    4.2 指定位置 filename::linenum
5. reverse debug (反向调试)
    A perfect example about reverse debugging supported by GDB can found in GDB Wiki, process record tutorial.
    see http://sourceware.org/gdb/wiki/ProcessRecord/Tutorial
